short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Customize your Rose-Hulman moodle page navigation menu sidebar

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Tired of having too many old classes listed on the sidebar navigation of your Moodle page? Look no farther this plugin allows you to add custom links to your Moodle sidebar navigation page. This is designed to work only for the Rose-Hulman Moodle page.
